124,/Hotel_Review-g186338-d1097114-Reviews-or120-CityStay_Hotel-London_England.html#REVIEWS,"CityStay Hotel Reviews, London",Excellent,"CityStay is excellent for both leisure and business travellers. Good transport links to the West End, Canary Wharf, Docklands and Victoria Park and easy access to local amenities. We stayed at the hotel for 4 nights and really enjoyed the hassle free comfortable atmosphere. Guests have access to the lobby and kitchen 24 hours to help themselves. Rooms are clean and nicely decorated. Real good value for money! We also hired a car from Enterprise, which is right across the road from the hotel. Will stay there again.",Date of stay: August 2008,5.0
